      "text": "In unix, you can compose operations by piping text between various tools.<p>What would it look like to be able to compose capabilities (as in [1]) in the same manner?<p>For example, if you wanted to build a capability that only allowed read-only access to files in  &#x2F;usr&#x2F;foo&#x2F;* in a certain date range?<p>If capability based security is to ever take off, this will have to be one of the building blocks. I&#x27;m having trouble even imagining what kind of syntax or tooling would be required.<p>[1] - https:&#x2F;&#x2F;en.wikipedia.org&#x2F;wiki&#x2F;Capability-based_security",
